Mhenni Xalifi

Mhenni Xalifi d yiwen n yilemẓi i d-yefka Udrar n Fad deg temnaḍṭ n At Smaɛel, ilul deg useggas n 1990. Ɣas yufa-d iman-is d ameɛḍur, ur yettekker ara, maca allaγ-is ibedd, yenjer abrid n Belɛid At Ʃli d wid icuban γur-s imi yesdukkel-iten-t i merra. Yessefra, yura, yecna.

D amedyaz, d amaru, d aneγmas s tutlayt tayemmatt (taqbaylit) akk d tefransist deg Uγmis n La Dépêche de Kabylie, d yisebtar n Tiγremt deg La Cité, d bab n umagrad ‘‘Nnhda n acer » d yimgraden-nniḍen i d-yettawi γef yidles d waddal, timetti, adiwen-nni, yimeɛḍar d tejmilin.

Yekki deg aṭas n temzizlin d tfaskiwin i d-yettilin deg tmurt n Yiqbayliyen γef tmedyazt (Tafaska n Udrar n fad) d tullisin (Tiregwa tasbeddit takanadit i tmaziγt).

Yewwi arrazen, yerna yessuffeγ-d yiwen uḍebsi n ccan azedgan s Teqbaylit anda yekki unaẓur ameqqran Zedek Mulud, yessnulfa-d arraz n umagrad ifazzen γef tudert n Dda Lwennas Meɛtub.

